      <title>瑞士人称食品价格上涨不是农作物贸易商的错</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/swiss-say-food-price-rises-are-not-the-fault-of-crop-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府表示，押注农作物期货的交易商并不是造成食品价格上涨的原因，投机行为反而可以帮助抑制市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/swiss-say-food-price-rises-are-not-the-fault-of-crop-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
