      <title>Archegos 的黄因震惊华尔街的罪行面临刑罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/archegos-hwang-faces-sentence-for-crimes-that-shook-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Archegos Capital Management 创始人 Bill Hwang 将于周三因欺诈和市场操纵被判刑，这与他价值 360 亿美元的家族理财室在 2021 年的惊人倒闭有关，这起案件引起了华尔街的极大关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/archegos-hwang-faces-sentence-for-crimes-that-shook-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金多斯称欧洲央行利率明显下降但需谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/ecb-rates-clearly-headed-lower-but-prudence-needed-guindos-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行副行长路易斯·德金多斯表示，欧洲央行将进一步降低利率“显而易见”，但由于贸易紧张局势加剧和全球冲突等不确定因素，官员们不应仓促推进这一进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/ecb-rates-clearly-headed-lower-but-prudence-needed-guindos-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Vista 即将以 24 亿美元的价格出售 LogicMonitor 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/vista-said-to-near-logicmonitor-stake-sale-at-2-4-billion-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Vista Equity Partners 即将达成协议，将 LogicMonitor Inc. 的少数股权出售给一群投资者，该交易对该 IT 基础设施监控平台的估值约为 24 亿美元，包括债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/vista-said-to-near-logicmonitor-stake-sale-at-2-4-billion-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
