      <title>十月份交易推迟后，阿达尼再次发行美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/adani-offers-dollar-bond-again-after-earlier-deal-was-postponed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的企业集团上个月因部分投资者反对定价而推迟了债券发行，但周三该集团的美元债券销售订单量超过 19.5 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/adani-offers-dollar-bond-again-after-earlier-deal-was-postponed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 01:27:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
